{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "I53PQFGZZ265L766G66ZFRBZBENN6ZNF",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "501078513",
    "title": "そよ風を超えて",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "勝負服をテーマにした雑誌の特集に\nヤマニンゼファーが掲載されることになった。\nその取材に彼女と共に臨んだのだが――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "pathId": 5859159637495560926,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いやぁ、近くで見ると\nますます可愛さが際立つ勝負服ですね～！\nでは、キュートなポーズいってみましょう！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 176,
                    "pathId": 9002648387064208380
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 249,
                    "pathId": 1375935277936113641
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -988765907692176396,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "キュート……\n花信風の如く、ですね。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -7539419012571075220
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": 6332820647937911508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1313738422829559392,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "モチーフはお花ですか？\nふわふわしていて、\n可憐なゼファーさんにはぴったりです！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 1825167884776356785
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -3759113121362266593
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7671544745670849975,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "これは風です。\n私のなりたいと思う憧れを形にしたもので――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": -8516055029461245989
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -8797063722766808040
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6448505260027087554,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "なるほど風！\n確かに、そよ風のような爽やかさが\n感じられて素敵ですね！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -3379670682930543604
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -6162995401907306320
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8872831048576652013,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……ありがとうございます。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": -5033669089015936363
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -697387062886907200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4746937301761410875,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『あなたにとってはそうなんですね』と\nいった感じで相槌を打つヤマニンゼファー。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -4127875622898235616
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 341012186612726051
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -827965122954517250,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そんな彼女を見守りながら、\n勝負服のデザインを決めた時のことを\n思い出していた。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -7071090257451062479
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -573360509912309328
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5556269081816399367,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "勝負服に取り入れるモチーフ……ですか？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "夢や理想を込めている子が多いけど",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 8129203702284736975
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": -7487192849016215621
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 2281574103992290778
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 4648658948230953503
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3119745244641397093,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "夢や理想……ならば私は、風です。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -8333502044231154989
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 7031739123603932087
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2912983591149097328,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "かつて見たレースで浴びたような、\nどこまでも自由で、純粋で、鮮烈な風。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 3766335259244669166
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 2553711648055959384
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -528730564966518876,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "強く速く、私の心をさらっていった\nあの疾風のようになりたい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ならそのレース場に行ってみよう！",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 4132433107877010263
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 5322738377349821637
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1411873915658696663,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "かつてヤマニンゼファーが憧れを抱いた\n場所――そこに行けば、勝負服のデザインが\nより明確に固まるだろう。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": 3150269114646555847
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -694252310489669609
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5509369832044842863,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "耳をすまし、目を閉じれば……\nあの時の風と光景が鮮明に蘇ります。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 154,
                    "pathId": -7638188997189441626
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 5251979468485592331
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 614594494595625,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……ああ、そうだ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 3135181202641153930
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -890700453832539265
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3838301446032402257,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "疾風と共に自由に揺れるひだ飾り、\nひらひらと舞うリボンの軌跡を目で追って――\n心は朝風のように踊り、高鳴ったのです。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "pathId": -2700205697697753285,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "（ワアァァァッ！！！！！）",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 3913714704634470174
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 3832787423303950516
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1887919357498147371,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……っ！\nこの風は――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 4206435169691656660
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 5120474041859998211
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8113213446348452871,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふふっ。今も昔も、ここには\n素晴らしい雄風が吹いていますね。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -7100323743052694259
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": 6614690492397934013
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8829709619999063326,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "私の想いもまた……当時と変わらず\n心の中に吹き続けています。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -7723719338920928536
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -2290717657357100560
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1592931871234238445,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "変わらぬ憧憬、ゆるぎなき恒風……\nきっとそれが、私の勝負服という風なのです。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "素敵な勝負服になりそうだね",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -1200032864147426539
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -5240287206116184995
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6440500707518537809,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……はい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -5164333989163715424
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -3003112947351579091
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1887383989682748726,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの時の誇らしそうな彼女の笑みを思い出し、\n誤解されたまま撮影を終わらせたくない\nという気持ちがわき起こる。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "走っているところを見てもらおう、ゼファー",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 214,
                    "pathId": -6171564844479305800
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 287,
                    "pathId": 1462035532373874583
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -5365437190465568418
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -6803914049368353060
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 68038414589678880,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "えっ？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -592199463822604655
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 7165900142117282100
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 7717698493207229779
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3872337089746056284,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ヤマニンゼファーの風は、記者が思うよりも\n強く、速く、見る者の心を惹きつけるものだ。\n――そう訴えた。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ゼファーはそよ風なんかじゃ収まらない",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "彼の心をさらってやろう",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 36
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 5049671507805008498
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 3255660585820799254
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -2762735786314651478
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8367685470788114134,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさん……。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 2553179119900588404
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": -8299690166207052690
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -3120272624460929029
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5642143854981131159,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あなたは……私という風を正面から受け止め、\nあるがままを感じてくれるんですね。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 3540254970802747221
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -8498932452871839404
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1618200822844574427,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "はあああああっ……！！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -1713242910029943056
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2483854341470944456
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5733274735308731421,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こ、これは……！！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "pathId": 1433786164393170288,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ゼファーさん！　すみませんが、\nもう1度撮影させてもらっても\nよろしいでしょうか！？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 214,
                    "pathId": -7252868860923712980
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": 5516335515522351857
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7394637829051145715,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "記者A",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "私は誤解していたみたいです。\n貴方の風は――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -407669837384832951
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -5375910181898885395
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7333123644452995319,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『そよ風、というには強烈すぎた』\n……ですか。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君の風を理解してもらえたみたいだね",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 34
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": 5054214580621966883
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -5085029681540207842
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -743804758678974273
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": -7223605946639157753
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3725024820597874237,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "はい。……けれど、私は今よりもっと強く、\n雄大な風になってみせます。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -5137633930286479367
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -4716260422275375342
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": -8098141754144236578
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4782395692715153038,
            "blockIdx": 34
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どこまでも自由に駆け、\nいつの日か、やがて理想へ届くように。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -5271589297393802578
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -945986679784570770
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": 2055568640541281461
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8586037253213574127,
            "blockIdx": 35
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……はい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 37,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7686790773948931721
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 325003860068358584
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -3904840686358792042
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4233475506793235933,
            "blockIdx": 36
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ヤマニンゼファー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの瞬間、私の心をさらった風のように――\nこの勝負服と共に、\n烈風の如く駆けてみせましょう。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 38,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -7323519381706422417
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": -1899591391944099291
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2839572870535899060,
            "blockIdx": 37
        },
        {
